WEBVTT

00:02.469 --> 00:05.221
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:05.221 --> 00:07.524
Well, I'm off, Sam.

00:07.524 --> 00:09.526
Sixth row center

00:09.526 --> 00:11.027
for the Royal Shakespeare Company.

00:11.027 --> 00:12.529
I still have the extra ticket

00:12.529 --> 00:15.532
if you happened to
have changed your mind.

00:15.532 --> 00:17.033
I-I just don't like that stuff.

00:17.033 --> 00:19.035
All those guys jumping around

00:19.035 --> 00:21.037
stabbing each other
in their leotards. I...

00:21.538 --> 00:23.540
I'm sorry.

00:23.540 --> 00:24.541
Come on.

00:24.541 --> 00:26.042
I don't want to go alone.

00:26.042 --> 00:27.043
I-I know. I know.

00:27.043 --> 00:28.044
Did I hear right?

00:28.044 --> 00:29.546
You're leaving early?

00:29.546 --> 00:31.047
I'm going to a play.

00:31.047 --> 00:34.551
Fine. I'll just stay here,
work my butt to the bone,

00:35.051 --> 00:38.054
while the boss's fiancée
takes another day off.

00:38.054 --> 00:39.556
SAM: Hey, come on. We're
not that busy around here.

00:39.556 --> 00:41.057
What're you doing?

00:41.057 --> 00:43.059
As a matter of fact, why don't...

00:43.059 --> 00:45.562
why don't you go to the play with Diane?

00:45.562 --> 00:46.429
Ha.

00:48.181 --> 00:49.682
How about it, Carla?

00:49.682 --> 00:52.068
We rarely do things together.

00:52.068 --> 00:54.738
We never do things together.

00:54.738 --> 00:56.189
It'll be fun.

00:56.189 --> 00:59.692
It'll broaden your horizons.

00:59.692 --> 01:00.693
You... what're you saying?

01:01.194 --> 01:02.195
I-I'm going to get the afternoon off

01:02.195 --> 01:05.197
if I go to the play with Bleachbag?

01:05.197 --> 01:07.700
Only if you go to the
play with Bleachbag.

01:07.700 --> 01:08.501
It's a deal.

01:08.501 --> 01:10.920
(laughs): I'm so excited.

01:10.920 --> 01:13.373
I've been waiting months for
this production to arrive.

01:13.373 --> 01:14.758
Sounds good.

01:14.758 --> 01:16.509
Bye-bye.
Bye-bye.

01:16.509 --> 01:18.711
I'll bring the pork
rinds, you bring the beer.

01:19.796 --> 01:22.632
We'll make spit wads
out of the programs.

01:23.516 --> 01:26.853
Take this. Follow her. Enjoy.

01:27.854 --> 01:30.356
Hey, honey, wait up.

01:33.276 --> 01:37.113
(piano plays)

01:37.113 --> 01:39.365
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:39.365 --> 01:42.368
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:42.368 --> 01:45.371
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:45.371 --> 01:48.374
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:48.374 --> 01:54.130
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:54.130 --> 01:56.916
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:56.916 --> 02:01.921
? Where everybody knows your name ?

02:01.921 --> 02:06.926
? And they're always glad you came ?

02:06.926 --> 02:08.928
? You want to be where you can see ?

02:08.928 --> 02:11.931
? Our troubles are all the same ?

02:11.931 --> 02:16.936
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

02:16.936 --> 02:19.939
? You want to go where people know ?

02:19.939 --> 02:21.941
? People are all the same ?

02:22.442 --> 02:26.946
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

